comment: Harris (ORL) sets the screen on Carter-Williams (MIL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Vucevic's (ORL) hand inadvertently gets caught in Pachulia's (MIL) jersey and the contact is incidental and has no affect on his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Multiple players from both teams enter the lane prior to the release of the FT.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with Ilyasova's (MIL) arm and body from behind and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) and Pachulia (MIL) make incidental contact during rebounding.
Oladipo (ORL) jumps into the legal defender Middleton (MIL) on the jump shot and there is incidental contact.
There is incidental contact between Pachulia (MIL) and Oladipo (ORL).
L-Slash shows Harris (ORL) has his arm on Middleton's (MIL) waist and makes incidental contact that does not affect his shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) commits a take foul on Oladipo (ORL).
Middleton (MIL) makes contact with Oladipo's (ORL) arm and body and the contact affects his movement to the basket and layup attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot.
